    "entry": "CONTEXT_SUMMARY.md",
    "title": "Claude Code Expert",
    "summary": "Bootstrap context for a high-intelligence Claude Code expert plugin (v6.0.0) with 16 commands, 33 skills, 16 agents, and a 10-tool MCP server covering deep code reasoning, orchestration, CI/CD, enterprise security, model routing, context budgeting, and interactive tutorials.",
